reviews.reviewText: I love writing letters to friends, it’s a forgotten art with all the instant messaging.This paper is lovely, and matches my gold ink pen too. It is lined however, I initially thought they would all be portrait lines but it’s a mix of portrait and landscape lined and blank paper. So I guess good for bullet journaling too.
